str ftime
Code       Meaning                     example 
%d         day(zero-padded)            30
%m         mounth (zero-padded)        07
%Y         Year (4 - digital)          2025
%y         Year (2-digit)              25
%B         Full mouth name             July
%b         Abbreviated nounth          Jul
%A         Full weekday name           Wednesday
%a         Abbreviated weekday         Wed
str ptime
Code       Meaning                     example
%H         Hour                        03:   
%M         Minute                      :45
%S         second                      43


Operation          example 			
add 10 days     date +timedelta (days - 10)
subtract3 weeks     date - timedelta(weeks -10)
add 90 minutes     datetime + timedelta(minutes - 90)
time difference between two dates  date2 - date1 -> returns a timedelta
get total seconds in duration      delta>total_seconds()
